title: Epic Reborn
description: Epic Reborn Free Manhua Chen Lei was destined to fail due to fate, however he was reborn and returned to his youth. Where his family hadn’t been destroyed, and his parents and loved ones had yet to die a tragical death… Chen Lei is determined to make up for his regrets! With the memories of his past life, with his peerless talent, Cheng Lei will embark on a long journey against the heavens! Protect the family, crush the enemy, and the world’s treasures are in my hand! Lying on the knees of a drunk beauty, awakening the power of the world, becoming a supreme, invincible emperor!
